    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031880/extras/4fcd4a859c1bd118e885e1a14aa8b91c.avif?t=1770896486\" width=369 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大汽公司雇佣你在毫无防备的城镇居民中制造对汽车的泛滥需求！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设计有史以来最精妙的停车场，然后说服市民这对他们必不可少。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传播吸睛的汽车宣传广告，智胜那些讨厌的反汽油抗议者，把安静的社区变成你的泊车帝国！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是时候提高汽车销量和油耗了！为了利润……但主要是为了自由！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031880/extras/d243c7cf9dce805584835c9038641c09.poster.avif?t=1770896486\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031880/extras/d243c7cf9dce805584835c9038641c09.webm?t=1770896486\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031880/extras/d243c7cf9dce805584835c9038641c09.mp4?t=1770896486\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031880/extras/c8662c0e17958ec0ee753a249a8a37f7.avif?t=1770896486\" width=369 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特性</strong>：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即时模拟数百车辆和（秃头）市民。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买土地，拆除房屋，建造你梦想中的停车场：铺开无尽的平坦沥青海洋，或用3D建造工具在空中建造。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解所有人的想法：他们是开始拥抱汽车了？还是对你不断上涨的停车费和石油钻机感到恼火？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用汽车宣传广告让所有人燃料入脑。布置闪亮的雕像、广告牌海报，并用扩音器播放朗朗上口的口号。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以某种方式让人们满意：如果交通状况一团糟，那就用你辉煌的摩天轮来分散他们的注意力！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制反汽车抗议，别让他们毁了你的商誉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在数据面板上追踪一切：真正的大亨喜欢看到数字上涨。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >钻取石油。满满的油罐，满满的爱。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >公共交通竞争：你不想看见依赖火车或步行的城镇，你想要每个角落停满汽车！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >模组功能：如果你会使用Lua，就能在一定程度上修改内容和脚本。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031880/extras/e6a4f9b9a6b938221edab4e27d3e1ec2.avif?t=1770896486\" width=369 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《泊车之都》将策略模拟与讽刺融为一体，对汽车依赖和城市发展进行了社会评论。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为真正的大亨，打造你的汽车天堂！</p>",
